summary: My sister and I sister watched Michiko and Hatchin a while back and I decided it was high time to draw this hottie-patottie in...
caption:
My sister and I sister watched Michiko and Hatchin a while back and I decided it was high time to draw this hottie-patottie in all her glory. I would 100% recommend watching this anime if you haven’t, the art of it is honestly amazing and the story is really well done(I have a few grips but they’re small). Plus it actually does strong female characters right so that’s a huge plus! 

 I couldn’t decide which I liked more so have both!

blog.name: brambles-hearts-blog
blog.title: Bramble's Heart's Blog
blog.description:
This is a random blog about randomness shit.
Art/Ask/RP/18+ blog/Multifandom
Post are mostly drawn and/or written.
There will be gore, dark themes, and cursing. But mostly just funny shit.
I draw video games, IRL stuff, random fandoms and NSFW, sometimes. Lots of stuff really.
Response is usually fast unless I'm doing something. Might have to wait for an hour or so. But if it's something big, like going to the hospital or a tragedy, I usually post about it after the event has passed or when it's less stressful.
Roleplay is private (NSFW and/or SFW). I RP mostly one liners to paragraphs. Genre is an open bag for me.
Also sorry for the bad art. I'm just using what I have and to the best of my ability.
Anonymous are allowed!
(Description may change randomly. Scatter brained a bit.)
Enjoy!

tags: I don't know how I can properly convey how incredibly grateful I am
title: My Status
body:
Car: Repaired

Money: Enough leftover to purchase fabric for a quilt commission with enough to last us until payday (February 22)

Home: Phone connects to WiFi and informs me I’ve sold a quilt

Me: OMG A QUILT SOLD!!!!!!!

Quilt:

This has been a wonderful and productive day!

THANK YOU!!!  Thanks to the generosity of strangers, friends, and family we were able to get our car repaired, pay all the bills on time, put fuel in the car, and go to the fabric store for quilt materials.  I’m so very grateful for your aid and kindness.  I’m currently trying not to scream because my cats will be very startled.  You are wonderful!

This will be shipping tomorrow afternoon. 

If any of you would like to see what work I have available for purchase please check out my shop here.  All my work is handmade.  I make modern macrame jewelry (and can make a 100% metal-free piece for you) and quilts of all sizes.  After you receive your purchase please leave a review.  Thanks!

summary: Various sketches from a self insert rp I've been doing recently. I really missed my junker self insert oc, and it's really fun...
body:
Various sketches from a self insert rp I’ve been doing recently. I really missed my junker self insert oc, and it’s really fun to develop the friendship between me and Jamison. We’re best friends:)

I want to make a model sheet of my overwatch self insert, cuz it’s still really rough, as you could see from the blue pencil sketches. I’ll get there eventually tho
